dct_title_s: World iron ore supply and demand, December 1972
dct_description_sm: North Decimal Degree 85.000000 South Decimal Degree -85.000000 East Decimal Degree 180.000000 West Decimal Degree -180.000000 Summaries of world iron ore supply and demand, 1970, and principal world iron ore loading and discharging ports. Shows iron ore trading routes and consumption and production statistics for various countries. Includes tables.
